OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773551082
OL,3,CMinisters accused of using 'hugely
OL,4,Cinflated' jobs figures for data centres
OL,6,FThe UK Government is using "hugely
OL,7,Finflated jobs estimates" in order to
OL,8,Fjustify the construction of hyperscale
OL,9,Fdata centres, campaigners have claimed.
OL,11,FCountryside charity Action to Protect
OL,12,FRural Scotland (APRS) highlighted
OL,13,F"preposterous" figures on the
OL,14,Femployment created by such
OL,15,Fdevelopments.
OL,17,FIt now wants to see "far more scrutiny
OL,18,Fof the claims" from both the
OL,19,FGovernment and developers with regard
OL,20,Fto data centre jobs.
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@XO]uD@AOUuD@NO]yD@UOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773551082
OL,3,CMinisters accused of using 'hugely
OL,4,Cinflated' jobs figures for data centres
OL,6,FAPRS issued the plea as it published a
OL,7,Freport on the issue, but the UK
OL,8,FGovernment insisted the research
OL,9,F"fundamentally misrepresents how jobs
OL,10,Fare counted for major infrastructure
OL,11,Fproject".
OL,13,FIt comes weeks after UK Technology
OL,14,FSecretary Liz Kendall visited
OL,15,FScotland's first AI growth zone in
OL,16,FLanarkshire, claiming developments
OL,17,Fthere could create 3,400 jobs in the
OL,18,Fcoming years.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773551082
OL,3,CMinisters accused of using 'hugely
OL,4,Cinflated' jobs figures for data centres
OL,6,FAPRS said it is concerned the
OL,7,FGovernment is not estimating jobs
OL,8,Faccurately ` citing the case of the
OL,9,F#10 billion AI growth zone announced
OL,10,Ffor Northumberland in 2024.
OL,12,FThe APRS report said while the
OL,13,FGovernment had said the zone would
OL,14,Fsupport 4,000 jobs, "later
OL,15,Fclarification revealed that this total
OL,16,Fincluded 1,200 construction roles and
OL,17,F2,700 indirect and induced jobs,
OL,18,Fmeaning the data centre itself would
OL,19,Fonly directly employ 100 people".
OL,26,@vD@UOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773551082
OL,3,CMinisters accused of using 'hugely
OL,4,Cinflated' jobs figures for data centres
OL,6,FAPRS also analysed data centre
OL,7,Femployment in northern Virginia in the
OL,8,FUS, which has the "largest
OL,9,Faccumulation of data centres in the
OL,10,Fworld, constituting 13% of all
OL,11,Freported data centre operational
OL,12,Fcapacity globally".
OL,14,FHere it found investment into data
OL,15,Fcentres had totalled 71 billion US
OL,16,Fdollars (#53.4 billion) in the past
OL,17,Fdecade, adding this "dwarfed
OL,18,Finvestment in other sectors" such as
OL,19,Fmanufacturing which had received 34
OL,20,Fbillion US dollars (#25.6 billion).
OL,26,@pD@SOUtD@RO]yD@UOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773551082
OL,3,CMinisters accused of using 'hugely
OL,4,Cinflated' jobs figures for data centres
OL,6,FAPRS ` which is already calling for a
OL,7,Fmoratorium on new hyperscale data
OL,8,Fcentres in Scotland ` said: "Data
OL,9,Fcentre investment was extremely
OL,10,Fineffective in creating jobs, creating
OL,11,Fonly three jobs per 100 million US
OL,12,Fdollars invested."
OL,14,FIn contrast, it said manufacturing in
OL,15,Fthe area had created 168 jobs for the
OL,16,Fsame investment.
OL,18,FAPRS director Kat Jones said: "It's
OL,19,Fabout time the hyperscale data centre
OL,20,Fdevelopers were called out on their
OL,21,Fludicrously inflated job projections.
OL,26,@pD@]OUtD@RO]zD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773551082
OL,3,CMinisters accused of using 'hugely
OL,4,Cinflated' jobs figures for data centres
OL,6,F"Data centres famously employ
OL,7,Fextremely few people, and have
OL,8,Fenormous environmental impacts, so we
OL,9,Fshould expect more scrutiny of exactly
OL,10,Fwhat benefits hyperscale AI data
OL,11,Fcentres would bring to Scotland.
OL,13,F"We have found that data centres tend
OL,14,Fto employ far fewer than 100 staff,
OL,15,Fusually between 20 and 50, but we are
OL,16,Fbeing told that the proposed
OL,17,Fhyperscale data centres will each
OL,18,Fcreate thousands of jobs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773551082
OL,3,CMinisters accused of using 'hugely
OL,4,Cinflated' jobs figures for data centres
OL,6,F"Developers and the UK Government seem
OL,7,Fto be taking the actual estimate of
OL,8,Fjobs, adding temporary construction
OL,9,Fand indirect employment, and then
OL,10,Fassume that each of these jobs create
OL,11,Fup to six additional jobs. This is the
OL,12,Fonly way we think it would be possible
OL,13,Fcome up with these preposterous
OL,14,Ffigures.
OL,16,F"The developers and the Government
OL,17,Fneed to stop using hugely inflated
OL,18,Fjobs estimates to justify these
OL,19,Fhyperscale data centres.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773551082
OL,3,CMinisters accused of using 'hugely
OL,4,Cinflated' jobs figures for data centres
OL,6,F"They will have to find a more
OL,7,Fplausible reason to legitimise the
OL,8,Fsheer quantities of energy, land and
OL,9,Fwater that will be diverted from the
OL,10,FScottish economy at large, to the
OL,11,Fpurpose training US big tech's AI
OL,12,Fmodels."
OL,14,FA UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"This report fundamentally
OL,16,Fmisrepresents how jobs are counted for
OL,17,Fmajor infrastructure projects.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@HO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773551082
OL,3,CMinisters accused of using 'hugely
OL,4,Cinflated' jobs figures for data centres
OL,6,F"We have never claimed that thousands
OL,7,Fof people will work inside a data
OL,8,Fcentre day to day. Our figures include
OL,9,Fconstruction, supply chain and wider
OL,10,Fjobs across the economy, which are
OL,11,Freal roles that bring real benefits to
OL,12,Flocal communities.
OL,14,F"AI data centres are enabling
OL,15,Finfrastructure, like energy networks
OL,16,For transport. Judging them solely on
OL,17,Fpermanent on-site headcount ignores
OL,18,Fthe investment, capability and job
OL,19,Fopportunities they unlock.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773551082
OL,3,CMinisters accused of using 'hugely
OL,4,Cinflated' jobs figures for data centres
OL,6,F"The alternative is to send that
OL,7,Fgrowth and those jobs overseas, while
OL,8,Fbuying back the compute from abroad."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
